metadata.name: VALOR
metadata.description:
THE BEAR SYMBOLIZES STRENGTH, PATIENCE, COURAGE, AND HEALTH.

THE BABOON SYMBOLIZES CURIOSITY, PARENTHOOD, COMMUNICATION, AND SOCIABILITY.

THE LEOPARD SYMBOLIZES AGILITY, ELUSIVENESS, SELF-RELIANCE, AND RARE BEAUTY.

THE COMBINATION OF SUCH STRONG-WILLED BEASTS REPRESENTS WHAT IT TAKES TO CONQUER LIFES CHALLENGES. TO BE ABLE TO TAKE ON ANYTHING WITH FIRMNESS AND BRAVERY. TO BE STRONG IN MIND, BODY, AND SPIRIT.

TRADITIONALLY PAINTED
WITH HYPERREALISM TECHNIQUE
USING ACRYLIC ON 80X80 CANVAS
